{"tid":136439,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【柒出國際】港警出醜到德國 德傳媒報道自比猶太受害者言論","createTime":"2017-02-27T05:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T05:32:08.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e02aa7c06d64c2577b30c5e968d56c10761911ae","tid":136439,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:14:14.000Z","msg":"七警罪成被判囚兩年，觸發警察員佐級協會及警務督察協會早前舉行「特別代表大會」，逾3.3萬人出席，集會上其中一名發言警員以猶太人被德國納粹逼害自比，惹來二戰涉及國家的炮轟，包括德國領事館亦在facebook刊登聲明批評，希望警員們能多看歷史。<br />\n<br />\n德國媒體亦有報道事件，德意志廣播電台（Deutschlandfunk）引述香港警員在大會上自比如在納粹時期的德國猶太人，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>並報道示威背景是源於2014年傘運時，7名警員毆打示威者罪成判囚，社會引起警察過度使用武力及撐警的對峙。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n報道引述德國駐港領事館在facebook作回應，批評警員相關類比言論完全不恰當，發言警員是對嚴重缺乏對史實的認知，亦指以色列駐港總領事館已發聲明批評「不恰當」及「令人遺憾」。<br />\n<br />\n報道文末指香港警方希望調解爭議，稱據傳媒報道，警方希望向兩個領事館澄清，有關言論不代表警方立場，亦憂慮領事館會向特區政府作出投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警犬揚威海外 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5495d425e7891caa6bb6dbc0f813c1d9cbf369","tid":136439,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:14:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170227/56359730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170227%2F56359730&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6aNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=7181c24f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170227%2F56359730&h=00c225d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170227/56359730</a><br />\n<br />\n補Link <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10eb0b8641fae2e73c39e2652714261b8ad9bb11"